{"tid":783114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩坐796c然後入左一大班蝻","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T16:57:23.000Z","uid":40965,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4bf23483af8781c77e3add67f96a52d7ae5debe","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"仲有兩件肥婆腩<br />\n應該係班蝻仔既老母<br />\n然後班蝻又嘈又臭 又郁黎郁去（架車好迫）<br />\n跟住有個黑色背心 拎把直遮 個樣勁霸氣<br />\n然後用把好沉好穩定既聲 啤住班蝻仔實一實 然後：hey listen don&rsquo;t move<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個刻我好似見到李小龍打班日本仔既影子咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係巴打想話你知 你好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我全程車都望實你 我知你都留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非gay"},{"pid":"7435beed32805b2787375ca0c0f23e30a29f6202","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"三個臭腩臭婆先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中一個腩仔用書包係咁頂到我<br />\n我一野批爭落佢個頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5584b4d204c0e1846192a168c0abe5b3f211d83b","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"補充返 佢拎住把遮格仔圖案<br />\n著短牛仔褲 有肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣有啲似泰臣 做話劇個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但佢係霸氣勁多 對眼殺得死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  170左右 途中我忍唔住望佢 佢望返我  我都嚇到縮一縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662976ebe619fde808e2923be2e8e84f3bd6509e","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"多謝你維護世界和平啊<br />\n如果要打架 我一定幫手打撚死啲蝻狗 <br />\n同趕三件肥婆落車 迫佢行路減肥去臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd12b1b31efeb47f75a55eac1c78ec4403db14bd","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"屌好撚嬲啊呢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a21685fb2675946f770647608e1b8fdf16a535","tid":783114,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662976ebe619fde808e2923be2e8e84f3bd6509e","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"多謝你維護世界和平啊<br />\n如果要打架 我一定幫手打撚死啲蝻狗 <br />\n同趕三件肥婆落車 迫佢行路減肥去臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122145d9abbeb218f56a00887b561cc64644c035","tid":783114,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime